Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.46,0:01:22.03,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}戴着无法飞翔的螺旋桨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.57,0:01:25.99,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,50)\blur3}抬头仰望着半分天空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.03,0:01:29.49,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}一路赤脚追逐着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.24,0:01:33.87,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,50)\blur3}始终如此的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.29,0:01:37.00,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,50)\blur3}也许一直在误解
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.29,0:01:40.34,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,50)\blur3}持有自信迎面生活
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.88,0:01:50.55,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}重要的宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.89,0:01:53.68,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}为了能够永久珍藏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.97,0:02:02.57,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}这份心情  一定会消失不见
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.61,0:02:05.74,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,100)\blur3}旋转起来吧
